OL,16,Fintroduced in 2011 and gave Welsh
OL,17,Fequal legal status with English as
OL,18,Fwell as stipulating it "must not be
OL,19,Ftreated less favourably." It replaced
OL,20,Fthe Welsh Language Act of 1993.
